item.title: Can someone tell me something with client
item.dc:creator: @pure_wc1994 pure wc1994
item.description:
@pure_wc1994 wrote:

Okay, I don’t know if this is entirely sure, but it worked for my friend

Right click Client and chose edit. Then with Ctrl + F search for Ip (If it comes up with something different keep hitting enter until you see the IP address) change the Ip address to your No-Ip one. If you haven’t made a No-Ip Ip I suggest doing so now

www.no-ip.com

Hope this helped.

~Pezza X
